The '''Wildlife Commission''' was a [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] commission that took care of many different kinds of wildlife. As the [[Hawk-bat/Legends|hawk-bat]] population on Coruscant lessened, they asked the [[Coruscant WeatherNet]] to start the summer earlier to improve the hawk-bat's mating cycle.

